notesStmt.note: Title and date from title page (p. 1).

msContents.summary: A collection of approximately 120 short poems, mostly love poems, followed by a table of contents of first lines.

supportDesc.extent: 106 leaves : 198 x 139 (175 x 107) mm. bound to 203 x 148 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Paper, iii (contemporary paper) + 106 + ii (contemporary paper) leaves; 1-109, 109-211; near-contemporary pagination in ink, upper outer corners. Earlier pagination trimmed away, but visible beginning around p. 60.
Paper, fol. ii + 106 + i; the pagination in ink appears as 1-109, 109-211, but there were two pagination systems, with many of the earlier numbers cropped but visible beginning around p. 60.

layoutDesc.layout: Written in single columns; frame-ruled in lead.

history.provenance: Bookplate once on title page was removed.
